        <item>
            <title>【评测】Threezero《心桥链结》小团　高性价比 + 连动设计有心思</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/mdlxdango/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mdlxdango</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/mdlxdango/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 05:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217960</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Threezero 的出品超越来越多不同系列，今次推出的《Kokone Link（心桥链接）》系列首款产品，名为「Dango（小团）」的小型机械人。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217962" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/snap0174-694x477.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="477" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/snap0174-694x477.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/snap0174.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC6431" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498290084/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498290084_24d80bc104_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6431" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此 Figure 取材自网络科幻小说，并以 1:1 比例制作，完美复刻小说中角色原貌。小团高约 9 厘米，其外观设计以白、蓝、金色调为主，以光面漆作涂装，特别是金色部份，很多细节及纹理都有表现出来，效果非常不错可见厂方的用心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6273-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6273-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6273.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217964" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6276-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6276-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6276.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>小团的体积虽然细小，但当中却设有总共 49 个关节，拥有合金骨架，部份部件也是合金制，虽然细细只但手感都几有份量，且保持良好可动性，关节也几扎实。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6302-412x580.jpg" alt="" width="412" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6302-412x580.jpg 412w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6302.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 412px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6309-452x580.jpg" alt="" width="452" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6309-452x580.jpg 452w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6309.jpg 702w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 452px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6304-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6304-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6304.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6305-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6305-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6305.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217969" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6307-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6307-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6307.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6312-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6312-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6312.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6455-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6455-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6455.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217974" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6320-429x580.jpg" alt="" width="429" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6320-429x580.jpg 429w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6320.jpg 666w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 429px" /></p><p>其中一个亮点是小团的眼球设计是可动的，可摆出可爱的 Pose；头顶被拉起时，就转换为战斗模式，连动式设计会令眼盖半闭，耳边的盔甲会展开；前额透明部份及双眼亦有 LED 灯，启动后加上战斗模式，设计非常有心思，令小编不得不赞。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217973" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_3028-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_3028-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/img_3028.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6314-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6314-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6314.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6317-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6317-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6317.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>其他 Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC6297" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498290209/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498290209_6aab1e580d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6297" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6321" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498290104/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498290104_94026a91fd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6321" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6351" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53497987041/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53497987041_024d445533_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6351" width="1024" height="694" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC6464 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53499531314/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53499531314_8bd0e3c5d0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6464 (1)" width="1024" height="792" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6452 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498342627/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498342627_e10dd7291d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6452 (1)" width="957" height="1024" /></a></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6461 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498342622/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498342622_e842a84c13_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6461 (1)" width="873" height="1024" /></a></p><p>配件方面，小团附有 4 Set 可换手势，及两款特效配件「蓝色光剑」与「黄色光炮」，提供更多互动性及可玩性。最具创意特别地方，附有一个锁匙扣配件，插好在背后，可将小团变身成为装饰或锁匙扣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217978" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6470-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6470-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6470.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217979" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6471-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6471-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6471.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217980" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6472-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6472-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6472.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6474-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6474-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6474.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217977" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6475-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6475-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dsc6475.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次 Threezero 的小团是一个新的尝试，虽然《Kokone Link（心桥链接）》这套小说不是太多人认识，但也见到厂方制作上的用心及诚意，而这个 Figure 的定价只是$200 有找 (早鸟预订优惠至 2 月 2 日)，可说非常抵玩高性价比。相信之后亦会有其他机体登场，期待这个新系列的发展。</p><p><a title="_DSC6333" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53498141863/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53498141863_4c0bfa6219_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6333" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/mdlxdango/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【评测】Threezero《心桥链结》小团　高性价比 + 连动设计有心思</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
